      "content": "but that's the thing, i don't feel like i matter to anyone here. it's not that i'm hurting people, it's just that i'm a zero. like, if a single drop of water falls into the ocean, does the ocean even notice? it's just easier to accept that everything is quieter when you aren't trying to force yourself into a world that doesn't have a space for you. don't you think there's a certain kind of logic in just letting go of the struggle?",
